<item>
            <title>[SOLR-1894] Solr Itas sample app does not work on multicore</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-1894</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The SolrItas sample app does not support multicore - it hard-codes the Solr URL to the default.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;comment about security removed - this issue is solely about fixing Itas to work natively on multicore&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12463163">SOLR-1894</key>
            <summary>Solr Itas sample app does not work on multicore</summary>
